.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, nectarine, orange, pineapple
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, musician, pilot, teacher
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, cat, goat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, thriller, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, subway, train
 1. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the architect##3
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 7. the teacher is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating orange is the owner of the cat##1
11. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
12. the owner of the goat is on the right of the pilot##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is the person eating pineapple##1
14. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | orange | nectarine | mango     | pineapple |
| Job           | pilot  | teacher   | architect | musician  |
| Pet   | cat  | goat      | pony     | hedgehog   |
| Movie-Genre         | western | zombie  | crime   | thriller    |
| Transport     | subway | roller    | train     | motorbike |

