.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, gardening, traveling
There 4 different types of food: grapes, cauliflower, blueberry, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, rock, trance
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, snake
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dannemann, aristoff, davidoff
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the fan of rock is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 4. the fan of trance is between the montecristo-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
 5. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
10. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
11. the person eating watermelon is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating watermelon##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
14. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
15. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | traveling | drawing    | board-games | gardening       |
| Food           | cauliflower | grapes  | watermelon   | blueberry |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | reggae     | trance      | rock            |
| Pet           | cat       | horse      | hedgehog    | snake           |
| Cigar     | davidoff      | aristoff | dannemann   | montecristo         |

