.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, blueberry, pepper, watermelon
4 different games are played: canasta, bridge, snooker, whist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, documentary, epic, romance
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, argentine, polish, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, skateboarding, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person eating blueberry##2
 2. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
 5. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the turkish is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 9. the person playing canasta is the person eating watermelon##1
10. the person eating blueberry is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person playing canasta is the person watching action movies##1
12. the polish is the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the argentine is in an even position##4
14. the person eating blueberry is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
| Food          | watermelon   | banana        | pepper      | blueberry      |
| Game           | canasta | snooker         | bridge   | whist |
| Movie-Genre   | action       | epic          | documentary | romance        |
| Nationality           | dutch         | argentine    | polish    | turkish         |
| Sport         | handball     | skateboarding | volleyball  | cycling        |

