.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapefruit, peach, raspberry
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, canasta, billiard
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, mechanic, teacher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, february, june
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the teacher is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing canasta##1
 6. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the analyst is the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating peach is the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
14. the analyst is between the person eating peach and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea    | 7up        | juice      | lemonade   |
| Food          | raspberry   | peach      | grapefruit | blueberry  |
| Game         | monopoly | canasta    | whist    | billiard |
| Job           | teacher     | accountant | analyst    | mechanic   |
| Birthday   | june | november     | may    | february  |

