 4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 7. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the person driving the trike is between the fan of metal and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 9. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the designer##3
13. the person driving the van is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
14. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
