The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, horror, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, punk, indie, trance
 1. the videographer is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of punk is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the fan of d&b is the dancer##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the videographer is between the fan of punk and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 7. the electrician is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the electrician##1
11. the person eating broccoli is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |    4     |
