.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, lemonade, sprite
There 4 different types of food: apricot, onion, orange, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, manager, analyst, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, sports, time-travel
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, grey, blood-red, coral
 1. the person who likes blood-red is the manager##1
 2. the manager is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person who likes grey is the analyst##1
 4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person who likes lavender is between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching sports movies##2
12. the person eating pepper is the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person who likes grey is on the far left or far right##3
14. the mechanic is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
